      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6 max-w-3xl">
        Bleeding-edge build from the main branch. Updated continuously with the latest changes. Not recommended for production use.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <div class="font-semibold text-text">ghcr.io/grc-iit/chronolog-dev:develop</div>
          <span class="inline-block mt-1 px-2 py-0.5 bg-white/10 text-text-muted text-xs font-semibold rounded">Rolling</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2">
